        "text": "=📋 *New Episode Ready for Review*\n\n*Title:* {{ $json.title }}\n*Pillar:* {{ $json.pillarLabel }}\n*Language:* {{ $json.language.toUpperCase() }}\n*Slug:* `{{ $json.slug }}`\n*Duration:* {{ $json.duration || 'TBD' }}\n\n*Quick Answer:*\n{{ $json.quick_answer }}\n\n_Approve to publish to thevelatium.com, commit to GitHub, and send newsletter._",
        "additionalFields": {
